    pandas_wrap(pyo::PyObject)

    Wrap an instance of a Pandas python class in the Julia type which corresponds to that class.

    Pandas.pyattr_set — Function.
    pyattr_set(types, methods...)

    For each Julia type T<:PandasWrapped in types and each method m in methods, define a new function m(t::T, args...) that delegates to the underlying pyobject wrapped by t.
